@startuml seq_03_forgot_password
title Sequence Diagram: UC-03 Forgot Password

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Auth Controller" as Controller
participant "Auth Service" as Service
participant "User Repository" as Repo
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis
participant "Email Service" as Email

User -> Frontend: Enter email for password reset
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/auth/forgot-password {email}
Controller -> Service: Request password reset
Service -> Repo: Find User by email
Repo --> Service: User found (Local auth)
Service -> Redis: Generate & store OTP (TTL 5m)
Service -> Email: Send Reset OTP email
Email --> Service: Email sent
Service --> Controller: Success
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Prompt for OTP

User -> Frontend: Enter OTP
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/auth/verify-reset-otp {email, otp}
Controller -> Service: Verify OTP
Service -> Redis: Check OTP
Redis --> Service: OTP matches
Service -> Redis: Generate & store reset token (TTL 15m)
Service --> Controller: Success (reset token)
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Prompt for new password

User -> Frontend: Enter new password
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/auth/reset-password {email, token, new_password}
Controller -> Service: Reset Password
Service -> Redis: Validate reset token
Redis --> Service: Token valid
Service -> Service: Hash new password (bcrypt)
Service -> Repo: Update User password
Repo --> Service: Password updated
Service -> Redis: Delete reset token
Service --> Controller: Success
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Redirect to Login Page
@enduml